'''Senjitsu''' (選日) refers to a system of determining auspicious and inauspicious days based on combinations of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Calendar annotations|ja|暦注|qq=draft}}. It is a general term that includes {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Seven-day week|ja|七曜|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Jūniji|ja|十二直|qq=draft}} (middle tier), {{ill|Twenty-eight mansions|ja|二十八宿|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nine Star Ki|ja|九星|qq=draft}}, and {{ill|Lower-tier calendar annotations|ja|暦注下段|qq=draft}}, among others. It is also called '''Taku-jitsu''' (擇日), '''Senjitsu''' (撰日), or '''Zasshū''' (雑注). The method of determining dates in calendar annotations is called {{ill|Senjitsu-hō|ja|撰日法|qq=draft}}. Many aspects of this system overlap with the contents of the ancient Chinese "[[:zh:萬年曆|Wànniánlì]]" (or ''Wànnián {{ill|Nongminli|ja|中国暦|qq=draft}}''), leading to the belief that it originates from the farmers' almanac<ref>{{Cite web |title=查詢農民曆─農民曆/農曆/黃曆｜科技紫微網 |url=https://ecal.click108.com.twindex.php/ |website=ecal.click108.com.twindex.php |access-date=2023-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=2023農民曆吉時查詢、黃曆通書黃道吉日查詢 - 農民曆查詢 |url=http://www.nongli.info/huangli/ |website=www.nongli.info |access-date=2023-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=子易預測網 - 擇日萬年曆 |url=https://forecasting.hk/calendar/ |website=forecasting.hk |access-date=2023-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=農民曆專有名詞 @ Gloria隨筆 :: 痞客邦 :: |url=http://andafansia.pixnet.net/blog/post/40052541 |website=Gloria隨筆 |date=2011-12-11 |access-date=2023-07-20 |language=zh-TW |last=Andafansia (Andafansia)}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=你應該懂的農民曆常識!搞懂「當日紀要」神祉、挑對日子趨吉避凶不求人 {{!}} 食尚玩家 |url=https://supertaste.tvbs.com.tw/hot/321211 |website=TVBS |date=2020-02-06 |access-date=2023-07-20 |last=TVBS}}</ref>. However, some aspects such as {{ill|Ichiryū Manbai Day|ja|一粒万倍日|qq=draft}} were independently created in Japan after the introduction of the farmers' almanac and lack historical credibility, as they do not exist in the original almanac.
